to finish the new ones.

292
00:26:05,564 --> 00:26:08,191
You can imagine
how we stand with our creditors.

293
00:26:11,403 --> 00:26:13,947
Now is not the time to be timid.

294
00:26:15,199 --> 00:26:18,743
