301
00:26:55,864 --> 00:26:57,407
I need to get going.

302
00:26:57,491 --> 00:26:58,658
Mmm. Of course.

303
00:27:03,539 --> 00:27:05,206
Thank you, Abby.

304
00:27:05,958 --> 00:27:07,000
For everything.

305
00:27:08,085 --> 00:27:11,713
Well, you cure my syphilis,
