311
00:27:49,418 --> 00:27:51,085
No sores or warts.

312
00:28:12,316 --> 00:28:13,858
What do you see?

313
00:28:14,818 --> 00:28:16,486
Nothing that's bad.

314
00:28:22,826 --> 00:28:24,786
- That's from me?
- Mmm-hmm.

315
00:28:26,038 --> 00:28:27,705
You're lucky.

316
00:28:27,790 --> 00:28:31,376
