the two other girls on mercury treatment.

317
00:28:31,460 --> 00:28:33,211
Thank you.

318
00:28:33,295 --> 00:28:35,838
If you ever have any burning,
itching, or pain down there,

319
00:28:35,923 --> 00:28:37,256
