333
00:29:40,404 --> 00:29:42,655
Whenever I chance to open one,

334
00:29:42,739 --> 00:29:45,116
I'm always convinced that I

335
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:48,411
suffer from whatever disease
happens to catch my eye.

336
00:29:50,164 --> 00:29:52,373
I don't think you'll suffer this one.

337
00:29:55,335 --> 00:29:56,878
Oh, God.

338
00:29:59,548 --> 00:30:02,383
It's just a disease of the uterus.

339
00:30:02,885 --> 00:30:06,179
Surely you're not unacquainted
with that part of the woman's body.

340
00:30:09,224 --> 00:30:12,310
Whatever do you mean, Nurse Elkins?

341
00:30:16,064 --> 00:30:19,400
