345
00:30:37,753 --> 00:30:39,629
My adrenaline research.

346
00:30:42,049 --> 00:30:44,759
I look forward to reading this
over the weekend.

347
00:30:46,720 --> 00:30:50,723
But if it's all I expect it to be,

348
00:30:50,807 --> 00:30:54,393
consider your position here
significantly improved

349
00:30:55,229 --> 00:30:57,188
and in short order indeed.

350
00:30:57,648 --> 00:30:59,690
I was hoping you'd say that.

351
00:31:02,444 --> 00:31:05,029
Here's a paper
published by the French Academy of Sciences

352
00:31:05,113 --> 00:31:08,282
