using radioactive substances,

353
00:31:08,367 --> 00:31:10,868
and it found that malignant tumors
are more susceptible

354
00:31:10,953 --> 00:31:13,788
to the influences of radiation
than normal tissue.

355
00:31:14,289 --> 00:31:16,916
And I was wondering
if it might be possible to use that fact

356
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:20,294
to isolate a tumor and improve
its chances of successful removal.

357
00:31:24,132 --> 00:31:26,425
An intriguing hypothesis.

358
00:31:28,637 --> 00:31:32,431
Let's talk about it after you've finished
your work with adrenaline.

359
00:31:39,731 --> 00:31:40,856
Well, we're all here.

360
00:31:40,941 --> 00:31:43,568
