from any legal responsibility.

369
00:32:07,676 --> 00:32:10,177
However, I believe it will still be necessary

370
00:32:10,262 --> 00:32:13,806
to buy out the residents of Park Avenue
whose homes were damaged.

371
00:32:14,433 --> 00:32:18,185
By my reckoning,
$1 million should do the trick.

372
00:32:18,270 --> 00:32:21,439
Can I rely upon you gentlemen
for a third part of it each?

373
00:32:21,523 --> 00:32:24,025
Henry, will that be a problem?

374
00:32:24,651 --> 00:32:26,569
No. No, it won't.

375
00:32:29,197 --> 00:32:31,741
I paid a visit
to Mr. Speight's residence

376
00:32:31,825 --> 00:32:34,327
