490
00:41:51,217 --> 00:41:52,593
That's what it says.

491
00:41:52,677 --> 00:41:55,429
That's what the man says it says.

492
00:41:56,264 --> 00:41:57,431
So again,

493
00:41:58,266 --> 00:42:00,809
