494
00:42:00,894 --> 00:42:02,519
Yes.

495
00:42:02,604 --> 00:42:05,689
Do his words matter?

496
00:42:05,773 --> 00:42:08,192
Do his laws matter?

497
00:42:08,276 --> 00:42:09,985
- Yes.
